    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "mcsfG4EE0t7b"
      },
      "source": [
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "## Part 2: Project Declaration\n",
        "\n",
        "Before building, declare your project details. This helps you plan and will be part of your submission."
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "w0aS3oMw0t7b",
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "outputId": "b5dd6f15-2c4d-497e-860e-cd48b7b53ae7"
      },
      "source": [
        "# ============================================================\n",
        "# TODO: Fill in your project details\n",
        "# ============================================================\n",
        "\n",
        "PROJECT_INFO = {\n",
        "    \"scenario\": \"Customer Support\",  # \"Customer Support\", \"Study Guide\", or \"Personal Interest\"\n",
        "    \"topic\": \"TechGadgets Online Store\",  # e.g., \"TechGadgets Online Store\", \"Machine Learning Fundamentals\", \"Italian Cooking\"\n",
        "    \"description\": \"A tool to help you pick out the best adapter for your laptop.\",  # 2-3 sentences describing what your assistant will help with\n",
        "    \"target_users\": \"Tech newbies, Min-Max enthusiasts, and Deal Hunters\",  # Who would use this assistant?\n",
        "}\n",
        "\n",
        "# Print your declaration\n",
        "print(\" PROJECT DECLARATION\")\n",
        "print(\"=\" * 50)\n",
        "for key, value in PROJECT_INFO.items():\n",
        "    print(f\"{key.replace('_', ' ').title()}: {value}\")"
      ],
      "execution_count": null,
